<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>HTML List Tags</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .box {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px gray;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>HTML List Tags</h1>

<div class="box">
    <h3>1. Ordered List (Numbered)</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Java</li>
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>HTML</li>
        <li>CSS</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="box">
    <h3>2. Ordered List with Type</h3>
    <ol type="A">
        <li>Apple</li>
        <li>Mango</li>
        <li>Banana</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="box">
    <h3>3. Unordered List (Bullets)</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Cricket</li>
        <li>Football</li>
        <li>Hockey</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="box">
    <h3>4. Unordered List with Style</h3>
    <ul type="square">
        <li>Red</li>
        <li>Blue</li>
        <li>Green</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="box">
    <h3>5. Description List</h3>
    <dl>
        <dt>HTML</dt>
        <dd>Used to create web pages</dd>

        <dt>CSS</dt>
        <dd>Used for styling web pages</dd>

        <dt>JavaScript</dt>
        <dd>Used for interactivity</dd>
    </dl>
</div>

<div class="box">
    <h3>6. Nested List</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Programming Languages
            <ol>
                <li>Java</li>
                <li>Python</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li>Web Technologies
            <ul>
                <li>HTML</li>
                <li>CSS</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

</body>
</html>
